For some fields I need to use OrderedDict for my JSON dumps. Currently I create a sub-class from the JSONType:

```python
class OrderedJSONType(JSONType):
    def process_result_value(self, value, dialect):
        if dialect.name == 'postgresql':
            return value
        if value is not None:
            value = json.loads(value, object_pairs_hook=OrderedDict)
        return val
```

