Looks like an issue with https://github.com/graphql-python/graphene-django/blob/master/graphene_django/fields.py#L57. `default_manager` is the correct, sliced, queryset. However, as it gets joined to the queryset from the custom resolver (`Reporter.objects.all()`), the filter's slice is ignored.

Tried fixing in PR #126 but couldn't find an elegant solution.

